		function onLoad() {
			// Populate the culture dropdown list with all the available cultures.
			var cultureDDL = document.getElementById('ddlCulture'),
					currentCulture = Localization.browserCulture(),
					cultures = Localization.cultures;
			for (var code in cultures) {
				var opt = document.createElement('option');
				opt.value = code;
				opt.innerHTML = cultures[code];
				if (code === currentCulture)
					opt.selected = true;
				cultureDDL.appendChild(opt);
			}

			cultureDDL.onchange = function () {
				bind(this.value);
			}

			bind(currentCulture);
		}

		function bind(culture) {
			document.getElementById('page_title').innerHTML = Localization.localize('page_title', culture);
			document.getElementById('msg').innerHTML = Localization.localize('msg', culture);
			document.getElementById('page_footer').innerHTML = Localization.localize('page_footer', culture);
		}
	</script>
